lity to post messages on Twitter as soon as you press \&quot;wake\&quot; button. It\'s a social alarm, isn\'t it?)))&lt;br&gt;Try! And you’ll like it!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Recent changes:&lt;br&gt;2 languages of GM Alarm applicaton (Russian, English)&lt;br&gt;2 storage localizations (English [en], Russian[ru])&lt;br&gt;Ability to post custom message on Twitter right after awakening  &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Latest version:  1.0 (for Android version 2.1 and higher)  &lt;/div&gt;  &lt;div class=\&quot;section screensh\&quot;&gt;  &lt;div class=\&quot;tit\&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;GM Alarm&lt;/span&gt; SCREENSHOTS&lt;/div&gt;  &lt;img src=\&quot;http://img.apkbrain.com/market/img/20110503100438518.png\&quot; alt=\&quot;\&quot; width=\&quot;320\&quot;/&gt;  &lt;img src=\&quot;http://img.apkbrain.com/market/img/20110503100439520.png\&quot; alt=\&quot;\&quot; width=\&quot;320\&quot;/&gt;  &lt;/div&gt;',`softlinks`=' market://details?id=net.alarm.activity&amp;referrer=utm_source%3Dappbrain%26utm_medium%3Dmobileweb%26utm_campaign%3Dreferral '
